SPCA Nelspruit still sells its Valentine’s “paw packets”. Treat the furry loves of your life this Valentine’s Day by getting them one of these special gifts from SPCA. These packets include a handmade toy, an animal treat and a human treat.  Each packet will cost you R50 and are for both cats and dogs. ALSO READ: Here are the region’s latest dam levels  These are sold until stock lasts, so get yours now to avoid disappointment! Proceeds go towards fundraising for the organisation’s kennels.